AquiferAdminBaseUri: Base URL of Aquifer Admin website
AquiferApiBaseUri: Base URL of the Aquifer Internal API

ConnectionStrings.ApplicationInsights: Application insights connection string. Get from Azure instance.

Ffmpeg.FfmpegFilePath: File path of ffmpeg executable (can be relative); if ffmpeg is in path then just use 'ffmpeg'.

MarketingEmail.Address: Email address that the new content email is coming from
MarketingEmail.Name: Name that the new content email is under when email is sent
MarketingEmail.ResourceLink: Link to resources in new content email template
